7.	For the term of this Amendment, Transwestern agrees to provide a
credit 
to the Shipper for quantities made unavailable due to an event of Force
Majuere 
declared solely by Transwestern.  The amount of the credit will be
calculated 
by multiplying the quantities made unavailable by the Discounted Rate.



